    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80f0-8d22-c5f3042c0061",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There is a big increase in tools and services that now create novel learning pathways for learners. In this scenario, the challenge becomes recommending the correct pathway to the correct student. The paper presents a recommender system that introduces recommendations via multimedia content. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80f0-8d22-c5f3042c0061",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
